
This website uses the Confeature framework:
	http://github.com/Skreo/confeature
You should rename the ISEPLive's root dir "app" and put it in the Confeature's root dir.

Required packages :
	apache2
	php5
	php5-gd
	php5-ldap
	php5-memcache
	php-apc
	php5-ffmpeg
	ffmpeg
	memmcached
	mysql-server
	
Required Apache mods :
	rewrite
	deflate
	headers
	expires

PHP config :
	upload_max_filesize = 700M
	post_max_size = 700M
